The Conjuring 2 is a 2016 American horror film directed by James Wan and written by Carey Hayes , Chad Hayes , Wan and David Leslie Johnson .
It is the sequel to 2013 's The Conjuring and the third film in The Conjuring franchise .
Patrick Wilson and Vera Farmiga reprise their roles as paranormal investigators and authors Ed and Lorraine Warren from the first film .
The film follows the Warrens as they travel to England to assist the Hodgson family , who are experiencing poltergeist activity at their Brimsdown , Enfield council house in 1977 which later became referred to as the Enfield Poltergeist .
The Conjuring 2 was released in North America on June 10 , 2016 .
The film received generally positive reviews from critics and has grossed over $ 320 million worldwide .
A spin-off film , The Nun , is scheduled to be released in 2018 with Wan and Safran producing .